        "comment": "In particular high altitudes wind-protected shady slopes: Distinct weak layers exist in the top section of the snowpack. <br/> <br/> On Wednesday it will be warm. Sunshine and high temperatures will give rise as the day progresses to increasing moistening of the snowpack. <br/> <br/> At intermediate and high altitudes there is still a very large amount of snow. At high altitude snow depths vary greatly, depending on the infuence of the wind."
